        {
            "title": "美國股市：伊朗戰事延宕加劇美股拋售 那斯達克100指數跌入回調",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於交易員擔心伊朗戰爭升級引發的油價飆升將拖累全球經濟，美國股市周五跌勢加劇。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500指數收跌1.7%，錄得連續第五周下跌，為2022年以來最長連跌，該指數跌至逾七個月低點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以科技股為主的那斯達克100指數下跌1.9%，較10月高點下跌超過10%，進入通常定義的回調</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道瓊工業平均指數在收跌1.7%後也進入回調</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衡量市場波動的VIX指數自4月以來首次收於30上方</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在美國和以色列周五轟炸伊朗核設施，伊朗在波斯灣展開報復後，布倫特升至每桶114美元</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為股市開始顯現疲態，對戰爭迅速解決的希望正在消退，」HB Wealth Management首席市場策略師Gina Martin Adams表示</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在標普500各板塊中，非必需消費品板塊跌幅居前，通信、科技和金融板塊均下跌逾2%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500工業指數下跌1.3%，較3月2日的高點下跌近11%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「最理想的情景並未實現，」Zacks Investment Management首席市場策略師Brian Mulberry表示。「現在市場開始考慮中間情景和最壞情景。對股市而言，最壞情況是到7月油價升至每桶100美元以上」</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務卿盧比奧稱對伊朗的戰爭將持續「數周而非數月」，並重申無需動用地面部隊</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但市場仍對戰爭將長期持續感到擔憂。《華爾街日報》報導稱，川普考慮向中東增派地面部隊人員至多1萬名</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價飆升加劇了通膨擔憂，並削弱了聯儲會短期內降息的理由，推動本周美國國債殖利率走高</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至收盤，標普500指數下跌1.7%，報6368.85點</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道瓊工業平均指數下跌1.7%，報45166.64點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">那斯達克綜合指數下跌2.2%，報20948.36點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">那斯達克100指數下跌1.9%，報23132.77點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">羅素2000指數下跌1.8%，報2449.695點</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Stocks Sink; Nasdaq 100 and Dow Industrials Enter Correction</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-47574930-b66c-3fa2-a363-6af2dda22a87-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Industrial Giants Enter Correction in Warning Sign for Stocks</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">VIX Closes at Highest Level Since April’s Tariff Turmoil</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B6%E5%AE%95%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE-%E9%82%A3%E6%96%AF%E9%81%94%E5%85%8B100%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%B7%8C%E5%85%A5%E5%9B%9E%E8%AA%BF-212209037.html",
